body:
Here it is - the official post for the all star game. This game has been handpicked by Barney and myself. It will be at 7PM again and we NEED streamers. Not recorders, streamers. If you can stream, please reply to this post ASAP. We will play Senex, which means that positions will be versatile and people will not be locked into these positions given.

The players and teams:

Teams are not decided yet - they will be as soon as Robo and I get together and pick our teams as we are the two captains. Defenders will be picked first. If you can not make it, PLEASE reply below asap - this time we were prepared 

Defenders
  • Robin_DD_J
  • Pope_panda
  • Spookeh
  • Zero9178
Offenders
  • Tazz (captain 1)
  • Ihze
  • Notal
  • Jive
Frontliners
  • Loo
  • Bmb
  • Caiiden
  • Ciaaren
  • Cyclops (captain 2)
  • Ingigo
  • Raging
  • Iron
  • Stimulating
  • Juanoh
  • MapDev
  • Pantai -
  • Sparkz
  • Remy
  • Emmaye
  • Budah
We hope for this to be streamed and I know for a fact I WILL be recording and it won't crash.

Thank you
